Challenge #17

1.
    a) Using tar, create an archive of /etc in the current directory.

    b) Display the contents of the archive searching for a specific file in the archive.

    c) Extract the archive in the current directory.

2. 
    a) Using tar, create a compressed archive of /etc using gzip in the current directory.

    b) Display the contents of the archive searching for a specific file in the archive.

    c) Extract the archive in another directory.

